abilities.name: Illuminate
abilities.description: Channels light energy, building power the longer it's channeled.  Once released, a wave is sent forth that deals damage and gives vision in its path.  The longer it is channeled, the more damage is dealt. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
abilities.upgrade_description: Allows Illuminate to heal allies during the day for the same amount as its damage values.

abilities.name: Blinding Light
abilities.description: A blinding light flashes over the targeted area, knocking back and blinding the units in the area, causing them to miss attacks.

abilities.name: Chakra Magic
abilities.description: Restores mana to the target unit and reduces cooldowns of all abilities currently on cooldowns by a fixed amount.

abilities.name: Will-O-Wisp
abilities.description: Summons Ignis Fatuus at the targeted area. Alternates on and off every second. When active, it causes all enemies near it to stare hypnotized at it. Can be attacked by units outside of the radius, dies after a certain number of attacks.
